{"id":2103,"date":"2019-06-13T06:55:33","date_gmt":"2019-06-13T06:55:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/doxy-wp.themeix.com\/?post_type=docs&amp;p=2103"},"modified":"2019-06-13T06:55:33","modified_gmt":"2019-06-13T06:55:33","slug":"writing-blog-post","status":"publish","type":"docs","link":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/docs\/writing-blog-post\/","title":{"rendered":"Writing Blog Post"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>\t\t\t\tTo create a new post in Doxy Jekyll Theme blog area, you should create a new markdown (.md) file inside the _posts directory or folder.\u00a0 Here following a post example with different configurations for a blog post page.<\/p>\n<div id=\"gist94366798\" class=\"gist\">\n<div class=\"gist-file\">\n<div class=\"gist-data\">\n<div class=\"js-gist-file-update-container js-task-list-container file-box\">\n<div id=\"file-2019-02-15-welcome-to-jekyll-md\" class=\"file\">\n<div id=\"file-2019-02-15-welcome-to-jekyll-md-readme\" class=\"Box-body readme blob instapaper_body js-code-block-container\">\n<article class=\"markdown-body entry-content p-5\">\n<pre><code>---\nlayout: post\ntitle:  \"Blog Post Title\"\ndate:   2019-02-15 18:51:30 +0600\ntags: [jekyll, update]\npost_image: https:\/\/placehold.it\/500x600\ncomment: true\nauthor_url: https:\/\/themeix.com\nauthor_designation: Ux\/Ui Designer\nauthor_bio: Wrute bio for post author\n---\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"gist-meta\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gist.github.com\/themeix\/01722b35478240251efa8be45179afe4\/raw\/1cbf474d15a68da65050b612db3ac20653d1ac84\/2019-02-15-welcome-to-jekyll.md\">view raw<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/gist.github.com\/themeix\/01722b35478240251efa8be45179afe4#file-2019-02-15-welcome-to-jekyll-md\">2019-02-15-welcome-to-jekyll.md<\/a>\u00a0hosted with &#x2764; by\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/\">GitHub<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h4>Change Post Sidebar Position<\/h4>\n<p>You can easily change your sidebar position from the post layout option.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6929 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/themeix.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/post-left-sidebar-e1548916781888.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"897\" height=\"307\" \/><\/p>\n<p>There are 2 post layout available in that theme. Use\u00a0<strong>post_left<\/strong>\u00a0for left sidebar and use only\u00a0<strong>post<\/strong>\u00a0for right sidebar layout\t\t<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/2103"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/docs"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/2103\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wp-doxy.themeix.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2103"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}